  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2022-05-26",
    "date": "2022-06-22T18:49:05Z",
    "text": "Informing Veterans on Education for Transitioning Servicemembers Act of 2022 or the Informing VETS Act of 2022\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to regularly promote the Veteran Readiness and Employment program by (1) sending a letter to each veteran entitled to the program that explains the educational benefits of the program, and (2) providing in each letter and online a side-by-side comparison of benefits between the program and Post-9/11 GI Bill educational assistance."
  },
